241
00:26:32,419 --> 00:26:35,526
We're still on the quest?

242
00:26:35,561 --> 00:26:40,284
Bilbo, my dear fella,
Let us have a little more light?

243
00:26:40,319 --> 00:26:46,005
Far to the East,
over ranges and rivers ...

244
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:50,149
beyond woodlands and wastelands ...

245
00:26:50,184 --> 00:26:53,447
lies a single solitary peak.

246
00:26:55,591 --> 00:26:58,926
The Lonely Mountain.

247
00:26:58,961 --> 00:27:05,743
Aye, Oin has read the portends,
and the portends say, it is time.

248
00:27:05,778 --> 00:27:10,202
Ravens has been seen flying back to the mountain,
as it was foretold.

249
00:27:10,237 --> 00:27:14,636
When the birds Beorn
return to Erebor ...

250
00:27:14,671 --> 00:27:18,370
The reign of the beast, will end.

251
