252
00:27:25,524 --> 00:27:29,184
Chiefest and greatest calamity of our age.

253
00:27:29,219 --> 00:27:34,440
Airborne fire breather. Teeth like razors
claws like meat hooks.

254
00:27:34,475 --> 00:27:37,640
