Do you not think, others would've read em too?

267
00:28:35,999 --> 00:28:42,203
Rumors have began to spread.
The dragon Smaug, hasn't been seen in 60 years.

268
00:28:43,845 --> 00:28:49,801
Eyes look East of the mountains.
Acessing..wondering...weight the risk-

269
00:28:49,836 --> 00:28:53,881
Perhaps the vast wealth of our people
now lies unprotected.

270
00:28:53,916 --> 00:28:57,927
Do we sit back,
while others claim what's rightfully our?

271
00:28:57,962 --> 00:29:01,509
Or do we seize this chance
