293
00:31:07,307 --> 00:31:11,101
And while the Dragon
is accustomed to the smell of dwarves ...

294
00:31:11,269 --> 00:31:17,562
the scent of hobbit is all but unknown him,
which gives us a distinct advantage.

295
00:31:17,727 --> 00:31:20,435
You asked me
to find the 14th member of this company,

296
00:31:20,604 --> 00:31:25,317
And I have chosen Mr. Baggins.
There's a lot more to him then appearance 've suggest.

297
00:31:25,482 --> 00:31:29,733
