than any of you know.

298
00:31:29,903 --> 00:31:33,237
Including himself.

299
00:31:36,946 --> 00:31:41,286
You must trust me on this.

300
00:31:42,407 --> 00:31:45,924
Very well,
we'll do it your way.

301
00:31:45,925 --> 00:31:46,925
No..no.
-Give him the contract.

