00:32:04,464 --> 00:32:07,453
I can not guarantee his safety.
-Understood.

306
00:32:08,404 --> 00:32:10,901
Nor will I be responsible for his fate.

307
00:32:12,911 --> 00:32:16,210
Agreed.

308
00:32:16,245 --> 00:32:21,196
Total cash on delivery. Upto but not exceeding
one 14th total profit, if any.

309
00:32:22,309 --> 00:32:23,401
Seems fair...

