I can't just go running off into the blue!

324
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:58,629
I am a Baggins, of Bag End!

325
00:33:58,664 --> 00:34:01,388
You are also a Took.

326
00:34:02,862 --> 00:34:07,659
Did you know that your great-great-great, great-uncle
"Bullroarer" Took was so large...

327
