You don't have to do this.
You have a choice.

350
00:36:05,673 --> 00:36:08,522
You have done honourably,
by our people.

351
00:36:09,815 --> 00:36:13,260
You have build a new life for us
in the blue mountains.

352
00:36:13,407 --> 00:36:17,295
A life of peace and plenty.

353
00:36:18,596 --> 00:36:23,501
A life that is worth more
