356
00:36:36,172 --> 00:36:39,577
There is no choice, Balin.

357
00:36:39,730 --> 00:36:43,211
Not for me.

358
00:36:43,359 --> 00:36:46,017
Then, we are with you, laddie.

359
00:36:47,672 --> 00:36:52,302
We will see it done.

