393
00:42:56,713 --> 00:42:58,664
Move on.

394
00:43:05,495 --> 00:43:08,340
You'd have to manage
without pocket handkerchiefs ...

395
00:43:08,505 --> 00:43:13,774
and a good many other things,
Bilbo Baggins.

396
00:43:15,071 --> 00:43:20,464
You are born to the rolling hills
