415
00:45:45,526 --> 00:45:50,193
lead by the most vile of all their race.

416
00:45:50,362 --> 00:45:53,499
Azog - the Defiler.

417
00:45:55,634 --> 00:46:00,652
The giant Gundabad Orc
had sworn ...

418
