435
00:48:50,978 --> 00:48:54,576
And I thought to myself then...

436
00:48:57,172 --> 00:49:01,309
There is one who I could follow.

437
00:49:03,655 --> 00:49:08,379
There is one,
I could call ' King '.

438
00:49:26,992 --> 00:49:29,769
And the pale ork ...

439
00:49:30,817 --> 00:49:36,505
